text: The Federal budget 2015–16 is the federal budget of Pakistan for the fiscal year beginning from 1 July 2015 and ending on 30 June 2016. The budget was presented in the Parliament by the Minister of Finance, Ishaq Dar on June 5, 2015. == References == Category:Nawaz Sharif administration Category:2015 in Pakistan Category:Pakistani budgets Pakistan federal budget Pakistan federal budget Category:2016 in Pakistan
title: 2015–16 Pakistan federal budget
